'''Swamp Maidens''' were an all-[[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]], generally considered to be some of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] best exotic dancers.

When [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] visited the port of [[Terminus/Legends|Terminus]], Han tried to remember the name of the cantina where two of them danced stating, "''it was down one of these arcades where the tourists never venture.''"

